mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Mario Kart 8 item probability in a mushroom only race:
- Items of different values can be obtained in Mario Kart
- Item drop chances are based on the distance between the player and first place
- As the race in mushroom only, only mushroom items are available
- Drop chances taken from https://www.mariowiki.com/Mario_Kart_8_item_probability_distributions (Versus Races, Mushrooms Only, drivers controlled by players)
